<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            color: #333;
            font-family: monospace;
            margin: 4em;
            font-size: 2em;
        }
        
        p, form, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, input, select, textarea, div, a, img, ul, ol, li {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        ul {
            padding-left: 1em;
        }
        
        h1, h2, h3, h4 {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #FF5500;
        }
        
        p {
            margin: 1em 0;
            line-height: 3em;
        }
        
        h2 {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #FF5500;
        }
        
        label {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        </style>
    </head>
<body>
<h1>Terraform &amp; Ansible Project Sample</h1>
<p>
    This project demonstrates using <i>to be continuous</i> Terraform (AWS) + Ansible templates !
</p>
<p>
    <ul>
        <li>environment type: <strong>{{ environment_type }}</strong></li>
        <li>environment name: <strong>{{ environment_name }}</strong></li>
        <li>public DNS (from Terraform): <strong>{{ lookup('env','tf_public_dns') }}</strong></li>
        <li>Generated by: <a href="{{ lookup('env','CI_JOB_URL') }}">{{ lookup('env','CI_JOB_NAME') }}</a></li>
    </ul>
</p>
</body>